| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4300 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 307f1acc-5695-5016-935a-9a7a0a6cc5ce"
